    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……これにしようかしら……\nこちらの品もいいですわね……",
      "startTime": 5.6333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2389.9999999999995,
          "startTime": 3.19
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2790,
          "startTime": 3.59
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6260,
          "startTime": 7.06
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2099.9999999999995,
          "startTime": 7.7333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "すず？　何をしているんだ？",
      "startTime": 8.9666662216,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "明日、放課後ティータイムのみなさんの所へ\n遊びに行くので、準備をしているのですわ",
      "startTime": 14.4141979441,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "遊びに行くのに手ぶらはマナー違反でしょう？\nですから、ここはスーパーアイドルらしく……",
      "startTime": 21.3666662216,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "スペシャルでゴージャスなお土産を持参して\nみなさんの度肝を抜いてみせるのですわ！",
      "startTime": 27.7666654587,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "お土産で度肝を抜く必要はないと思うぞ……\nそれで、何を持って行くつもりなんだ？",
      "startTime": 34.699998792,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "私が用意するお土産は、一口食べればほっぺが落ちる\n極上のスイーツですわ！",
      "startTime": 42.5333321254,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "放課後ティータイムのみなさんはいつも\n練習の合間にお茶会をしているそうです",
      "startTime": 47.6231264211,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "……お茶会の合間に練習しているのだったかしら？\nどちらにしても素敵な習慣です！",
      "startTime": 55.5333321254,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "素敵な習慣……なのか？",
      "startTime": 58.399998792,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "ですから、お茶請けになりそうなスイーツを\nお土産にすれば喜んでもらえるはずです",
      "startTime": 65.199998792,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "という訳で、今日の仕事帰りに\n寄りたい場所があるので付き合ってくださいまし",
      "startTime": 71.0611775667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "彼女達の舌をうならせる極上のスイーツを\n探しに行きますわよ～！",
      "startTime": 78.199998792,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（こんなに浮かれるなんて、まるで遠足前の子供だな）\n（それだけ明日を楽しみにしているってことか……）",
      "startTime": 86.1333321254,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4733.3333332999955,
          "startTime": 90.8666654587
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "着きましたわ！\nこの辺りは有名な洋菓子店が多いんですのよ",
      "startTime": 94.3102460169,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ここなら美味しいスイーツが手に入りそうだな\nそれで、どの店で買うんだ？",
      "startTime": 102.5190883291,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "そうですわね……例えば、あそこのお店\nテレビで紹介されているのを見たことがあります",
      "startTime": 110.099998792,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "こっちは有名なパティシエのお店で\nあっちは海外のセレクションで優秀賞を取ったお店です",
      "startTime": 116.0666654587,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "向こうの行列が出来ているお店は\nグルメサイトでランキング一位の……",
      "startTime": 122.55184835,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "……困りましたわね。どのお店も美味しいと評判で\nどれか一つに決められませんわ",
      "startTime": 131.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "それならいっそ、世間の評判は忘れて\nすずの好みで選んでみたらどうだ？",
      "startTime": 137.5000013352,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03-suz016.m4a",
      "text": "私の好みで選ぶ……確かに、それもありですわね",
      "startTime": 140.1333346685,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03-suz017.m4a",
      "text": "好きな物をオススメして、みなさんがそれを\n好きになってくれたら、私も嬉しいです",
      "startTime": 149.4666680019,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03-suz018.m4a",
      "text": "では、私の好きな物をお土産にしましょう\n私と軽音部のみなさんで『好き』を共有するのですわ！",
      "startTime": 157.1666680019,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03-suz019.m4a",
      "text": "という訳で、あそこのスーパーに行って\n私の大好物のポテトチップスを買い占めますわよ！",
      "startTime": 165.2666680019,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（しまった！）\n（そういえばすずはポテトチップスが大好きだった）",
      "startTime": 171.6000013352,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03-suz020.m4a",
      "text": "もたもたしていないで手伝ってくださいまし！\n棚のここからここまで全部かごに入れるのですわ！",
      "startTime": 180.7666680019,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（やれやれ……まあ、すずは楽しそうだし）\n（好きにやらせてみるか）",
      "startTime": 189.5666680019,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_03-suz021.m4a",
      "text": "この調子でお土産を買いまくりますわよ！\n明日の放課後ティータイムが楽しみですわ～！",
      "startTime": 195.5666680019,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
